</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Paw-some Pups Rescue</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="adopt.html">Adopt a Pup!</a></li>
                <li><a href="about.html" class="active">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="how_to_help.html">How to Help</a></li>
                <li><a href="success_stories.html">Success Stories</a></li>
                <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="hero-section">
            <h2>Our Story: Passion for Paws!</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the heart of Paw-some Pups Rescue! We're more than just a shelter; we're a community of animal lovers dedicated to giving every dog a second chance at a happy life.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="featured-dogs"> <!-- Reusing 'featured-dogs' style for general sections -->
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>Paw-some Pups Rescue was founded in 20XX by a group of passionate volunteers who saw a need for a safe haven for abandoned, neglected, and surrendered dogs. We believe every dog deserves love, respect, and a warm home.</p>
            <p>Our team works tirelessly, often volunteering their own time and resources, to ensure our dogs receive the best care. From medical treatments to daily walks and cuddles, we pour our hearts into their well-being.</p>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/F0F8FF/808080?text=Our+Team" alt="Picture of the Paw-some Pups Rescue team and volunteers" style="max-width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px; margin-top:20px;">
        </section>

        <section class="hero-section" style="background-color: #f0f8ff; color: #34495e;">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To rescue and rehabilitate dogs in need, providing them with veterinary care, proper nutrition, and socialization. Ultimately, our goal is to find them loving, permanent homes where they can thrive and be cherished family members.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="featured-dogs">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>**Compassion:** Treating every animal with kindness and empathy.</li>
                <li>**Integrity:** Operating with honesty and transparency.</li>
                <li>**Community:** Building a network of support for dogs and their new families.</li>
                <li>**Advocacy:** Speaking up for the voiceless and promoting responsible pet ownership.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We believe in the power of a wagging tail to bring joy and companionship into human lives, and we're committed to making that connection happen.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Paw-some Pups Rescue. All rights reserved. | <a href="#" style="color: #fff;">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>

</body>
